                        <note>
									
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Fragments of the book of Numbers, i.e. chapters 1:1-2:31; 15:39-19:6; 22:26-26:49; 29:17-30:1; 30:12-32:33; 33:32-to the end of the book, each verse being followed by the Targum and Sa'adia's Arabic translation in the Hebrew characters.</p>
									
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Text and Targum have the simple superlinear punctuation.</p>
								
                        
                        
                        
                        </note>
								
                        
                        
                        
